sent.orig: I plant was built in 1990, specializes in small gasoline engine cylinder gasoline aluminum manufacturing.
sent.trans: 我厂始建于1990年，专业从事小型汽油机的铝制汽油缸体的制造。

sent.orig: This paper introduced the function and industrial application of gasoline blending line system in gasoline production.
sent.trans: 介绍了汽油在线调合系统的功能及其在汽油生产中的工业应用。

sent.orig: When gasoline burns, gasoline and oxygen molecules combine to form new molecules.
sent.trans: 当汽油燃烧时，它的分子和氧气分子结合起来，形成新的分子。

sent.orig: Pyrolysis gasoline contents high alkene, so it can not be sold as commercial gasoline.
sent.trans: 裂解汽油烯烃含量高，不能作为商品汽油销售。

sent.orig: Gasoline station operators are required to join the local gasoline station commercial association.
sent.trans: 经营加油站业者，应加入当地加油站商业同业公会。
